data.description: Pride of ownership is shown in this fabulous 3 bed, 2 bath property in Glendale! Fall in love with a bright & spacious interior showcasing wood-look flooring, fresh soothing palette, vaulted ceilings, & a charming fireplace. The spotless kitchen boasts white shaker cabinets with crown moulding, granite counters, stylish tile backsplash, stainless steel appliances, & a peninsula complete with a breakfast bar, the perfect spot for quick snacks & morning coffees. Primary bedroom features soft carpet in all the right places, a private bathroom, & a generously-sized walk-in closet. Host fun gatherings & summer BBQs in the lovely backyard including a covered patio & a remarkable swimming pool! This value won't disappoint!
